reviewText: I am really please and happy to watch the dvd of Be Careful with my Heart cause it brings back all the sweet and happy memories of Sir chief and Maya and that alone is enough to keep me going and makes my day complete. The story focus on the night before the wedding and the bonding of the Delarosa family specially Maya and Kute. Love it cause it reminds me of my own family in the Philippines when I was still there .
Wife states this series reminds her of us, How, duh I dunno. Married 33 years and going strong......... Great Series
